dash/turn
> > signal switch but its away being painted. Mel 67 Samba

 Correct, 67 dashes are pre-cut with a rectangular hole.
But they are smaller than DIN size radios.....
DIN is approx 180mm x 50mm with square corners.
The 67 opening is 179mm x 45mm with round radius corners.
A DIN radio will not fit..... BTDT.
